title: Hit List
subTitle: Vijay's life turns into a living hell when a mysterious masked figure abducts his family. Forced into a dark world of violence, he becomes an unwilling assassin, targeting the kidnapper's enemies.

title: The Power of 3 Jai Luv Kush
subTitle: Separated at childhood, identical triplets, who find their calling in life, reunite after one of them kidnaps other two brothers for his own purpose.

title: Guna 369
subTitle: The life of Guna, a happy-go-lucky man, turns upside down when he is falsely framed for a murder and imprisoned. After his release, he sets off to hunt the real culprits and expose their crimes.

title: Khel A Team to Play
subTitle: Two rival brothers face off against each other as coaches from opposite teams to win the annual village football tournament.

title: Ghost
subTitle: When an inexperienced lawyer chooses to defend a young politician who is accused of murdering his wife, a spirit begins to pursue her.

title: Rishtey - A Grand Celebration
subTitle: After falling in love with each other, a man and a woman must overcome obstacles and the generation-long rift between their families.

title: Kalki
subTitle: Kalki, an intelligent police officer, is assigned to investigate the mysterious murder of Sekhar, the brother of Narsappa, who rules the Kollapuram village.

title: Sankranthiki Vasthunam
subTitle: When a renowned tech entrepreneur is abducted upon returning to India, a police officer seeks the help of her ex-boyfriend, a former cop living with his wife, to aid in the rescue mission.

title: Coolie No. 1
subTitle: A matchmaker sets out to teach Hoshiyar Chand a lesson while hilarity ensues when he asks Raju, a coolie, to pretend to be a millionaire.

title: Game Changer
subTitle: In the midst of a power struggle for the chief minister's post, an upstanding IPS officer enters the fray of politics to fight against its corrupt system.

title: Kanguva
subTitle: A tribal warrior's ancient struggle to save his people mysteriously intertwines with a modern bounty hunter's perilous quest, linking two eras in an epic adventure.

title: Kanguva
subTitle: A tribal warrior's ancient struggle to save his people mysteriously intertwines with a modern bounty hunter's perilous quest, linking two eras in an epic adventure.

title: Mahaveer No.1
subTitle: A young orphan, White, challenges the sly Adikesavalu for control of the Ongole market and his daughter. Their fight unearths a past of greed, injustice and a simmering quest for revenge.

title: Bombay to Bangkok
subTitle: Shankar, a chef, chances upon a pouch full of money and escapes to Bangkok instead of Dubai. There, he meets Jasmine at a massage parlour and falls in love with her.

title: Cycle Kick
subTitle: The lives of two brothers change when they find an abandoned bicycle. However, their happiness is short-lived when the two-wheeler is stolen from them.

title: Dhaakad
subTitle: Despite her reservations, Agent Agni takes up the mission to track and capture Rudraveer, a trafficker in India. However, the assignment soon takes her down unnavigated routes.

title: Daring Baaz
subTitle: Goutham resolves to reunite his grandfather with Sunanda, his estranged aunt. However, he chooses to pose as a driver to befirend her.

title: Hero The Bullet
subTitle: Shiva, a young man, is looked down upon by his father due to his irresponsible behaviour. He soon gets embroiled in a tussle with an egoistic gangster who threatens his family.

title: Ramaiya Vastavaiya
subTitle: A man is challenged to work in a field and produce a huge harvest by the end of the season in order to marry the love of his life.

title: Kisi Ka Bhai Kisi Ki Jaan
subTitle: Bhaijaan, the eldest of three siblings, refuses to get married to maintain harmony in his family. However, complications arise after his brothers conspire for him to fall in love.

title: Wanted
subTitle: A sharpshooter is caught between a gangster who wants him dead since he knows too much, the police who want him for the information he holds and his girlfriend who yearns for him to mend his ways.

title: Aho Vikramaarka
subTitle: A ruthless cop unearths a sinister mystery, compelling him to confront the villainous Asura and rescue the victims held captive in his clutches.

title: Aho Vikramaarka
subTitle: A ruthless cop unearths a sinister mystery, compelling him to confront the villainous Asura and rescue the victims held captive in his clutches.

title: Masss
subTitle: After a life-threatening accident, a man finds that he can communicate with the dead, and must decide whether to act on their advice.

title: Gangs of Madras
subTitle: A distraught woman decides to exact revenge on the ruthless gangsters who framed her husband during a police encounter, making her lose him and her unborn baby.

title: Ghajini
subTitle: Suffering from memory loss every 15 minutes, a heartbroken man uses photographs, notes and tattoos to keep reminding himself to punish his lady-love's murderer.

title: Koogle Kuttappa
subTitle: A conservative villager hates the idea of his son relocating to Russia for a job. However, when his son brings a robot to care for him, he develops an unlikely bond with the machine.

title: Bhimaa
subTitle: After some mysterious instances at a temple of historical significance, a detective visits the region to investigate and find out the truth behind the incidents.

title: Dhamaal
subTitle: Four lazy friends learn about a hidden treasure in Goa and set out to find it. However, a police inspector learns about their plan and begins to pursue them.

title: Krrish
subTitle: After discovering his father's truth, Krrish must reveals his superpowers to the world and becomes the masked superhero.

title: Supreme Khiladi
subTitle: A charitable trust faces threats from a powerful mafia leader who has set his eyes on its land. He plans to kill the legal heir to grab the wealth, but a brave taxi driver becomes an impediment.

title: Heropanti 2
subTitle: A vigilante is sent on a mission by the government to kill enemy troops. However, things go wrong when he's mistaken for the leader of the troops.
